{"tid":2119572,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"董建華說香港成就由幾代人打拼　絕非其他國家恩賜","createTime":"2020-07-22T07:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T10:31:04.000Z","uid":39464,"like":28,"dislike":152,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"1b419ceeba93dce48f721c74c197e458545a25c7","tid":2119572,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:34:11.000Z","msg":"董建華於一個網絡論壇致辭說，西方政客千方百計將國內的政治壓力轉到外交戰線，批評他們錯判形勢，在全球需要聯手抗疫，維護經濟和金融穩定時，反而設立貿易壁壘、切斷科學合作、實行經濟脫勾、打壓及圍堵政策，令國際地緣政治形勢更加嚴峻。<br />\n<br />\n董建華表示，香港作為國際都會，難免受外在因素衝擊，認為港人一定要冷靜思考，而且要具備沉著應對的戰略定力，以及迎難而上發展的信心。他指，香港的成就由幾代香港人打拼得來，絕對不是其他國家的恩賜。<br />\n<br />\n他說本港有豐厚實力及穩定根基，也不是肆意破壞的違法分子可以隨便摧毀，中央政府會全力支持和愛護香港，形容祖國屬香港的堅實後盾，又指中國屬疫情中復甦最快的國家，相信國家富強，就是香港繁榮穩定的最有力保證。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539238-20200722.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539238-20200722.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=a3902750\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539238-20200722.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=68726507\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539238-20200722.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e9a32d3741fd3f5e883bd734d1a9335c29c8c6a9","tid":2119572,"uid":24457,"like":126,"dislike":0,"score":126,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:35:32.000Z","msg":"其他國家=中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c71218dfa8f8db4e6fc980bd0c26086d1acb77","tid":2119572,"uid":79117,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:35:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3fec25acc824fbac7835c2cfa134d8e8e720d61d","tid":2119572,"uid":179409,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:35:53.000Z","msg":"老董做乜寸中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/w